174 A.3d 509 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. DANIEL J. SMITH, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-193 September Term 2017

079417 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001351-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
